Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:32.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:34.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.56,0:00:36.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:43.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你还好吗，伙计？\N{\fnArial\fs32}You okay, bud?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:45.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你看电影时睡着了\N{\fnArial\fs32}You fell asleep during the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:47.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我本想让你接着睡的，你睡着时可爱极了，\N{\fnArial\fs32}I was gonna let you sleep, you looked so cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:51.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但接着你哭了起来，这就不那么可爱了\N{\fnArial\fs32}but then you started crying, and that was less cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:53.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}不，我很好\N{\fnArial\fs32}No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:55.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我不知道为什么我开始哭了\N{\fnArial\fs32}I don't know why I was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.18,0:00:57.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我的梦并不算悲伤\N{\fnArial\fs32}My dream wasn't really sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:04.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦，天，看看几点的...还有我的土豪金新表！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, gee, look at the time... and my classy new watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.72,0:01:06.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}让我送你回家吧，伙计\N{\fnArial\fs32}Let's get you home, bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:09.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃，你没错过多少剧情\N{\fnArial\fs32}Aw, you didn't miss much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:11.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}原来外星人抓奶牛\N{\fnArial\fs32}Turns out they were abducting cows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:13.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}是为了它们的早餐麦片星球！\N{\fnArial\fs32}'cause they needed milk for their cereal planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:14.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸，\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad, before you go, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:15.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你走之前，\N{\fnArial\fs32}before you go,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:17.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我能问你点问题吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:19.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}好啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:21.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}妈妈有没有跟你谈起过...\N{\fnArial\fs32}Did mom ever talk to you about...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:23.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}粉钻石？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Pink Diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:25.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}有些事情\N{\fnArial\fs32}There were some things
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:27.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你妈不那么愿意提起\N{\fnArial\fs32}your mom didn't like to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:29.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我从没有向她询问过细节\N{\fnArial\fs32}I never pressed her for details.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:31.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}为什么？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:34.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}罗丝和我谈论过很多重要的事情-\N{\fnArial\fs32}Rose and I talked about tons of important stuff --
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:38.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}音乐，漫画，将脚伸进沙子里-\N{\fnArial\fs32}music, comic books, getting sand between your toes --
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.52,0:01:40.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你懂的，个人感受\N{\fnArial\fs32}you know, feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:43.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们年轻时都犯过错\N{\fnArial\fs32}We both made a lot of mistakes when we were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:46.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我认为迪斯科会重新流行起来，她坚决反对\N{\fnArial\fs32}I thought disco was coming back, she started a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:47.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我认为她感觉\N{\fnArial\fs32}I think she felt like
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:50.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}她必须告诉我她的一切，但我告诉她，\N{\fnArial\fs32}she had to confess everything to me, but I told her,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:52.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}“过去已经过去了”\N{\fnArial\fs32}"The past is the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:55.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}“重要的是现在的你”\N{\fnArial\fs32}All that matters to me is who you are now."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:59.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}而且她是一个神奇的，友爱的人\N{\fnArial\fs32}And who she was, was an incredible, loving being.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:01.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}晚安，爸爸\N{\fnArial\fs32}'Night, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.96,0:02:02.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}晚安，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs32}'Night, Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:12.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我又回到了这里\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:14.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}好吧，我猜我能看看周围的环境\N{\fnArial\fs32}Well, I guess I can look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.97,0:02:17.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这是哪？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:19.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这-这是...\N{\fnArial\fs32}What's -- what is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:22.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.54,0:02:23.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:29.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}对不起，我待会会收拾的！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Sorry, I'll clean that up later!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:31.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}当你告诉我你的梦时，\N{\fnArial\fs32}When you told me about your dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我就觉得耳熟\N{\fnArial\fs32}I thought it sounded familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:37.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}就是这个-桥子\N{\fnArial\fs32}That's it -- the Palan-kwin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:40.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}其实，这个读作“轿子”\N{\fnArial\fs32}Actually, it's pronounced "palan-keen."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:42.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}是宝石人们！\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's the Gems!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:43.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}他们肯定知道这是什么！\N{\fnArial\fs32}They've gotta know about this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:46.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}Whee! -Whoo-hoo!-Whoo！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:47.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:49.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}嘿，你知道这是什么吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hey, do you know anything about this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:50.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:55.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文，你应该知道真相，而真相是...\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven, you deserve to know the truth, and the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我完全不知道是什么\N{\fnArial\fs32}I have no idea what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:58.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我根本就没见过\N{\fnAri.al\fs32}I've never seen it before in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:01.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}让一下，紫晶，让我...\N{\fnArial\fs32}Excuse me, Amethyst. Allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:05.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃...其实...\N{\fnArial\fs32}Uh... W-well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:07.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这看起来像是\N{\fnArial\fs32}it appears to be an illustration
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:09.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}某些日记中常见的幻想\N{\fnArial\fs32}in some kind of journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:10.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}算了吧，你知道我指的是什么\N{\fnArial\fs32}Come on, you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:12.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我做梦梦到了这个！\N{\fnArial\fs32}I had a dream where I saw this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:14.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}康妮和我在想也许...\N{\fnArial\fs32}Connie and I were wondering if maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.32,0:03:16.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文，为什么你和康妮不-\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven, why don't you and Connie --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:17.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你们不能去！\N{\fnArial\fs32}You can't go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:21.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}为什么不呢？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:23.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}对啊，为什么？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yeah, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我以为从此你们会告诉我所有事情\N{\fnArial\fs32}I thought you were going to tell me everything from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:31.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦，史蒂文，我们-\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, Steven, we--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:33.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这和粉钻有关吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Does this have something to do with Pink Diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我已经知道妈妈打碎了她\N{\fnArial\fs32}I already know mom shattered her,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:38.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}所以这个有什么不能告诉我？\N{\fnArial\fs32}so what is it about this that you can't tell me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.62,0:03:41.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}停下，你让珍珠非常难受\N{\fnArial\fs32}Please, you're making Pearl very upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:43.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}不！是我非常难受！\N{\fnArial\fs32}No! I'm very upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:45.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们，不能，去\N{\fnArial\fs32}We're not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}罗丝不想让你看到那个地方\N{\fnArial\fs32}Rose never wanted you to see this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:49.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}罗丝想？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Rose wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:51.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那我想做的呢？！\N{\fnArial\fs32}What about what I want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:54.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我受够了所有人都对我撒谎!\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm sick of everyone lying to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}罗丝是我的母亲！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Rose is my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:58.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}所有人里，不是我最应该知道真相吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Out of anyone, don't I deserve to know the truth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:00.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}现在不行\N{\fnArial\fs32}This isn't the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:03.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我，不，管！我想去那里！现在！\N{\fnArial\fs32}I don't care! I want to go there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:04.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:07.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我对不起，我-我不应把书带来的\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm sorry. I -- I shouldn't have brought the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:08.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}不，你应该带来的！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yes, you should have brought it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:10.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}还好有些东西能提供信息\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's lucky something has some information
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:12.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}否则我不得不她们口中撬出来！\N{\fnArial\fs32}that I don't have to get out of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:16.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}康妮，我得带走这本书\N{\fnArial\fs32}Connie, I need to borrow this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:18.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}可以，只是一定要小心使用\N{\fnArial\fs32}Okay, just be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我一周之内还得还回图书馆呢\N{\fnArial\fs32}I gotta return it to the library in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}谢谢\N{\fnArial\fs32}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:22.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}等等，史蒂文，你要去-\N{\fnArial\fs32}Wait, Steven, where are you --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:28.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文，别-别走啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven, don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:30.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你一定要相信我\N{\fnArial\fs32}You have to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:32.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我不明白，石榴\N{\fnArial\fs32}I don't understand, Garnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:34.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}至少你一直对我是坦诚的\N{\fnArial\fs32}At least you're usually honest with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:36.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我真的很想这样，\N{\fnArial\fs32}I really want to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:39.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但如果我告诉你为什么你不能去，\N{\fnArial\fs32}but if I tell you why you shouldn't go,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:41.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你只会心头长草的\N{\fnArial\fs32}you'll only want to go more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:44.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}啊？！那现在我更想去了！\N{\fnArial\fs32}What?! Well, now I really want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:46.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我这张嘴啊～\N{\fnArial\fs32}- I shouldn't have said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:48.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你不能去，因为我不能跟着你\N{\fnArial\fs32}You can't go because I can't go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:49.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}为什么？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:52.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}石榴，为什么？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Garnet, why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:54.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我...我害怕\N{\fnArial\fs32}I... I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我-我-我不能离她太近\N{\fnArial\fs32}I-I-I can't get near her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:59.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}啊～“她”！，哪个她？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Ah, "her!" Her, who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:00.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃，干！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Ah, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:02.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}现在草长了一米多高了\N{\fnArial\fs32}Now I've made it more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:03.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文，求求你\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:06.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}请留下来...就当是为了我吧\N{\fnArial\fs32}Just stay here... for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:08.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我不会的\N{\fnArial\fs32}I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:11.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我知道\N{\fnArial\fs32}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:16.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:18.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸，我需要你的帮助！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad, I need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:19.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}一切正-\N{\fnArial\fs32}Is everything o--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:21.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我在梦里看到了一个地方-而且是真实存在的-\N{\fnArial\fs32}There's this place I saw in a dream -- and it's real --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但宝石人们不愿意告诉我任何信息！\N{\fnArial\fs32}but the Gems won't tell me anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:25.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那里和粉钻石有关\N{\fnArial\fs32}It has something to do with Pink Diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我知道你不想涉及到母亲的过去，\N{\fnArial\fs32}I know you didn't want to get involved with mom's past,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:29.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但我想知道真相！\N{\fnArial\fs32}but I want to know the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:31.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这难道一点都不重要吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Doesn't that matter at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:33.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这当然很重要！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Of course it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:35.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}真的？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:36.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}让我看看\N{\fnArial\fs32}Let me see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:39.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那么宝石人不愿意带你去？\N{\fnArial\fs32}And the Gems won't take you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:40.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}是的\N{\fnArial\fs32}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:43.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}刚好我知道个人会！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Well, I know a guy who will!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:48.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那么，宇宙一家要去韩国了\N{\fnArial\fs32}So the Universes are going to Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:49.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}谢谢搭我们过去，安迪叔叔！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Thank you for the ride, Uncle Andy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:51.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}啊，这不算什么\N{\fnArial\fs32}Ah, it's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:54.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}俗话说，家人要帮助家人...\N{\fnArial\fs32}Like they say, family helps family...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:57.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}寻找神秘的远古遗迹\N{\fnArial\fs32}find mysterious ancient artifacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这会非常重要\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's gonna be very serious work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:01.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}没时间闲逛\N{\fnArial\fs32}No time for fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:04.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}不过，就没时间稍稍享受一下？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Well, isn't there time for a little fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:32.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}谢谢！蛤？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Kamsahamnida! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:33.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}干嘛这么着急？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What's the hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:34.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}就是这里\N{\fnArial\fs32}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:37.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你确定？\N{\fnArial\fs32}You sure this is the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:41.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}是的，虽然很难解释，但我能感觉到\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yeah. It's hard to explain, but I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}嗯...这里还挺漂亮的\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hmm, sure is pretty here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:46.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}所以有东西让你感觉熟悉吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}So does any of this look familiar to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文？喔，你还好吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven? Whoa, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:50.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你又开始流泪了！\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's happening again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:52.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我很好，咱们接着走\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm fine. Let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:54.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}算了，一起休息下吧\N{\fnArial\fs32}Come on, let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:56.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我觉得这座山真的影响了你\N{\fnArial\fs32}I think this mountain's really messing you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:57.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}不，爸爸\N{\fnArial\fs32}No, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:06:59.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这只可能意味着我们在接近！\N{\fnArial\fs32}This can only mean we're getting closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:00.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}来吧！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:03.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}看！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:06.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这看起来很熟悉啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}This feels familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:09.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸，帮我翻过围栏\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad, help me jump the fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦，天，我们上吧\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, boy. We're doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:14.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}喔，你老爸不能再像以前那样翻墙了\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, your dad really can't jump fences like he used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:20.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸，看那个！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:22.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}就是这里了！\N{\fnArial\fs32}This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但这个不一样啊？！\N{\fnArial\fs32}But it's different?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:29.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}在我梦里，它完全损坏了，而且是粉色的\N{\fnArial\fs32}In my dream, it was all broken down and pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:30.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这个看起来很新\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's in perfect condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:33.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}也许它从做了喷漆？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Maybe it got a paint job?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:34.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦，小粉\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, Pink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:39.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我对不起你，我实在对不起你\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:42.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我本来能做的更好的\N{\fnArial\fs32}I should have done more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:44.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}小黄说一切很快会结束的\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yellow says it'll all be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我在想你是怎么认为的\N{\fnArial\fs32}I wonder what you would think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这是你的星球，毕竟\N{\fnArial\fs32}This is your planet, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:52.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}至少我是这么想的\N{\fnArial\fs32}I still think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文，你认识她吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven, do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:07:57.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}喔，伙计！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Whoa, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:08:00.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我的梦-我是从她的眼里看到的\N{\fnArial\fs32}My dreams -- I was seeing through her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我流的是她的泪！\N{\fnArial\fs32}I've been crying her tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:05.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你去那里做什么？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What are you doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:08.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我感觉听到了什么人\N{\fnArial\fs32}I thought I heard someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:10.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}别急，我能搞定\N{\fnArial\fs32}Don't worry, I'll handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:12.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我认为这里不止我们\N{\fnArial\fs32}I think we're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:17.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}嘿！呃，今天天不错，不是吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hey! Uh, nice day out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:19.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我-我没看到你，\N{\fnArial\fs32}I -- I didn't see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:22.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你...呃...你好？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What's, uh... what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:24.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}珍珠？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Pearl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:27.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我的钻石，我发现了个土著人\N{\fnArial\fs32}My diamond, I've found a native.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦，呃，对！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, uh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:31.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我就来自这里！\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm from here, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:34.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}“你好”，陛下\N{\fnArial\fs32}Annyeonghaseyo, your highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}带他过来\N{\fnArial\fs32}Bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:41.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸，不要！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:45.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}多有趣啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}How curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:48.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我很惊讶人类\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm impressed by humanity's ability
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:49.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}在野外生存的能力\N{\fnArial\fs32}to survive in the wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:52.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}多么奇怪的星球\N{\fnArial\fs32}What a strange planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:57.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}还有哪里，一个脆弱如人类的存在还活着\N{\fnArial\fs32}Where else would a being as fragile as a human live,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:03.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}而强大如钻石的却已消逝？\N{\fnArial\fs32}while a being as powerful as a diamond perish?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:06.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}就是在这里...\N{\fnArial\fs32}This is where it happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:09.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}她被打碎的\N{\fnArial\fs32}where she was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:11.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你说完了吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Were you close?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:13.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}很快了\N{\fnArial\fs32}Very.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:16.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}噢，我非常抱歉\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, I'm awfully sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我能理解想继续生活有多难\N{\fnArial\fs32}I know how hard it is to move on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:20.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}当你失去你关心的人时\N{\fnArial\fs32}when you've lost someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:22.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}真的？\N{\fnArial\fs32}You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:29.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我也失去了一个对我非常重要的人\N{\fnArial\fs32}I lost someone very important to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我每天都在思念她\N{\fnArial\fs32}I miss her every single day,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:33.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}每时每刻都是\N{\fnArial\fs32}and I think about her all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:36.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但，她并不会回来了\N{\fnArial\fs32}But she's never coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:39.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这种感觉很难承受\N{\fnArial\fs32}That feeling can be so hard to be okay with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:42.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我很惊讶一个人类\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm surprised that a human being
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:45.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}能理解我的感受\N{\fnArial\fs32}is capable of understanding how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}真是羞愧啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:51.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你的星球孕育着一个致命武器\N{\fnArial\fs32}There's a geo-weapon incubating in your planet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:53.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}它将很快摧毁一切\N{\fnArial\fs32}that will destroy everything shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:57.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但，你不应承受这些，不是吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}But you don't deserve that, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:00.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}致命武器，对吧？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Geo-weapon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:03.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你知道，我真的不应该出现在车里\N{\fnArial\fs32}You know, I really shouldn't be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:06.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但我很高兴我来了，最，后，一，次\N{\fnArial\fs32}but I'm glad I came back one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:10.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我可以最后再挽救她一次遗产\N{\fnArial\fs32}I can save one last piece of her legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦，是吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, yeah? Oof!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:22.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那真是个巨大的胳膊啊！\N{\fnArial\fs32}That's a big arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}把我放下来，求求你了！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Put me down, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦！喔！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:31.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}将我放下吧，陛下！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Put me down, your highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.18,0:10:33.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}Whoa! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:34.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸，爸爸！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:40.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}停下！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:49.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸...\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:56.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文，我-我对不起！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven, I'm -- I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:56.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}石榴！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Garnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:57.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我“看到”你来了这里\N{\fnArial\fs32}I saw you come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:10:59.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我“看到”蓝钻石在地球上\N{\fnArial\fs32}I saw Blue Diamond on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:01.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我“看到”她见到我并找到了我们所有人\N{\fnArial\fs32}I saw her see me and find all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:03.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我不能和你出现在这里\N{\fnArial\fs32}I couldn't be here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:04.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}她抓走了我爸爸！\N{\fnArial\fs32}She took my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.46,0:11:07.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这都是我的错，我本该听你的话的！\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's all my fault. - I should have listened to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们该怎么办，石榴？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What are we gonna do, Garnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:13.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们要前往深空，我们要将他救回来\N{\fnArial\fs32}We're going to space. We're going to get him back.
